{"tid":2126440,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C.朗拿度追平祖記塵封86年單賽季入球紀錄+復賽射手榜第一位","createTime":"2020-07-26T23:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T20:05:13.000Z","uid":173952,"like":18,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"0371a5831c16d2839268faa8c688c9f1f8dc5769","tid":2126440,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T23:48:17.000Z","msg":"祖記2-0戰勝森多利亞，C.朗拿度表現十分出色，不但幫助球隊取勝奪冠，也追平了祖記隊史紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n  上半場補時階段，祖記獲得自由球機會，比真歷主射突然選擇橫敲，C.朗拿度心領神會，在禁區內抬腿推射，皮球應聲飛入球門死角。<br />\n<br />\n  在攻入這粒入球後，C.朗拿度今季的意甲入球數來到31球，追平了博雷爾（1933/34賽季創造）保持的祖記隊員意甲單賽季入球紀錄（31球）。<br />\n<br />\n  C.朗拿度的表現並沒有就此結束，第67分鐘，C.朗拿度射門造成對方門將脫手，巴爾納代斯基補射幫助祖記擴大比數。<br />\n<br />\n  在今場入球後，C.朗拿度在復賽後已經攻入10粒入球，超過史達寧（9球）、利雲（9球）等射手，獨享歐洲五大聯賽球員復賽射手榜第一位的位置。"},{"pid":"bf13e4c1b88eb1bdf217a4dc68a8e26c489ac441","tid":2126440,"uid":173952,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T23:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/sports/transform/618/w410h208/20200727/1e9b-iwxpesx1208082.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsports%2Ftransform%2F618%2Fw410h208%2F20200727%2F1e9b-iwxpesx1208082.gif&h=10f88427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又tapin"},{"pid":"16c95f35566faf3b144ea9e9a1142cd2177326bb","tid":2126440,"uid":12628,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bf13e4c1b88eb1bdf217a4dc68a8e26c489ac441","tid":2126440,"uid":173952,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T23:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/sports/transform/618/w410h208/20200727/1e9b-iwxpesx1208082.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsports%2Ftransform%2F618%2Fw410h208%2F20200727%2F1e9b-iwxpesx1208082.gif&h=10f88427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又tapin"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T23:51:50.000Z","msg":"又撚得幾靚喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},